thread.title: Jasmine Andres

author: Jasmine Andres
title: Jasmine Andres
text: My boyfriend and I are looking for a new place since our current place got flooded. We are moving into my moms and needed to find a cheap affordable storage unit. Its a bit stressful but using Sparefoot helped me find the best deals in my area and i was able to compare the deals. Some deals even had a free moving truck which i could cross off my list (last time i had to pay $150 for someone to move our things down 4 blocks). I was looking for an affordable 10x10 unit but they were all over $250 which is way out of our budget. I found a 8x8 unit and it was only $114 with a moving truck!! Super worth it and I found it through Sparefoot.
